Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,给我吧  给我吧  给我吧  给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sock it to me. Sock it to me. Sock it to me. Sock it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:19.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你脑子里还能有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What else do you have on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:27.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我在神游\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Swimming in my mind at this time, literally,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:31.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,思绪从我最新研究的水栽籼粳混合稻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is my new hydroponic indica-sativa hybrid,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:34.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,一路通过阿姆斯特丹快速通道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a touch of the mythic AK-47
