Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,它被烘焙成了香蕉面包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's baked into this banana bread
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,又被灌入了这个可以抹平的果酱之中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and infused in this potent spreadable jam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:46.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,这对于孤独的创造者来说再理想不过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's ideal for creative sojourns of a solitary nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,思绪泛滥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wheels up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jerry,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,吃自家旅馆东西的创始人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a prophet is without honor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,是不会获得别人的尊敬的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who eats his own profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:59.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,那可不对  本老弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not indeed, brother Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,这让我状态正佳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It puts me in a groove,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:03.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有人知道我什么时候会累\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and where it stops, nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:07.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝你再也不插手宾馆的工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank God you are no longer in the hotel business.
