Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:13.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的最新合规合法的业务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, my new legally sanctioned business
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,是把我们的税收翻三倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is tripling our revenue.
