Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}露西·布伦南
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我想找杜鲁门警长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello. I'd like to see Sheriff Truman.
