Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,哪一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,杜鲁门警长不在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sheriff Truman isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:44.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道哪一个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, do you know which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能会弄错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It could make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:47.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个生病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One is sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,另一个去钓鱼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the other one is fishing.
