Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,是关于保险的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's about insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:03.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定我能否帮上你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not sure I will be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要见杜鲁门警长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd like to see Sheriff Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:13.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会留下我的名片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll leave my card
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,改天再打电话来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and call in another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会留好名片的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll keep the card,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是除非\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but unless--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你以为你在往哪里走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where the hell do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:12.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, lookee here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:16.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,奥蒂斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Otis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:28.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  比尤拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Buella.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:33.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:36.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尤拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Buella,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:38.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,雷和达雅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ray and Darya--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:41.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,你把他们带回来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}have you got them back there somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去叫他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:46.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有  比尤拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, Buella,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:50.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,装饰一下你的前门吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}put something better at your front door.
