Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:12.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,达雅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Darya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:32.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,雷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ray,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:34.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,达雅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Darya,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:37.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:24:00.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,C先生  C先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. C. Mr. C.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:03.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,再见  奥蒂斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See ya, Otis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.20,0:25:53.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,特雷茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Tracey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.22,0:25:56.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,他不在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:25:58.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,没人在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No one is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.13,0:25:59.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.33,0:26:47.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.24,0:26:49.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,他去哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.14,0:26:52.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,这说明我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does this, by any chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.43,0:26:54.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟你一起进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}mean that I can go in there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.27,0:26:56.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我又带了两杯拿铁来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I brought us two lattes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.33,0:27:01.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.40,0:27:04.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,既然没人来阻止你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}since there's no one here to stop you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.50,0:27:07.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想你可以进来一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess you could come in for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.97,0:27:10.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道如果保安回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I don't know how you're gonna get out
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.22,0:27:11.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎么出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if the guard comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.34,0:27:15.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们先别去想这种可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's not overthink this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.32,0:27:54.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.70,0:27:56.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个玻璃箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A glass box.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.14,0:28:00.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是用来做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, but what's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.66,0:28:03.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.83,0:28:06.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是我帮学校做的一个活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just a job I got to help with school.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.80,0:28:16.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,这地方是谁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whose place is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.48,0:28:19.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,听说是个亿万富翁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I heard a billionaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.64,0:28:22.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,某个匿名富翁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some anonymous billionaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.04,0:28:24.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,好神秘啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:42.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我得留心观察这个箱子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm supposed to watch the box
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.80,0:28:45.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,以防里面出现些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and see if anything appears inside.
