Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.17,0:28:49.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,会有东西出现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do things appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.15,0:28:52.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,从开始到现在  我什么都没看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I haven't seen anything since I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.20,0:28:54.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我取代的这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But the guy I replaced,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.72,0:28:57.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,他看到过一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he saw something once.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.66,0:28:58.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.58,0:28:59.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,他不肯告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wouldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.60,0:29:01.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,或是不能告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or couldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.07,0:29:05.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不该说起这个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're not supposed to say anything about this place
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.53,0:29:06.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,或是那个玻璃箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or that glass box.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.90,0:29:18.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,好多设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a lot of equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.83,0:29:20.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,是不是某种科学实验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is it some sort of science experiment
