Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.75,0:29:28.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.80,0:29:54.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.84,0:29:57.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,给  你的咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here's your coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.88,0:29:58.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  特雷茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks, Tracey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.59,0:30:56.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要亲热一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you want to make out a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.02,0:30:58.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think?
