Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.29,0:35:59.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.36,0:36:01.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.76,0:36:03.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,是  我知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes,  I know this.
