Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.82,0:36:34.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was a funny thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.02,0:36:35.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话给你们的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't remember my address
