Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.26,0:37:25.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,女士  这里的管理员有钥匙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ma'am, is there a manager on-site with a key?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.89,0:37:27.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I don't know.
