Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.01,0:37:42.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是普通的医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}not the regular hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.22,0:37:48.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,达琳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, uh, Darlene,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.42,0:37:52.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,派个开锁匠来箭头路1349号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we're gonna need a locksmith over at 1349 Arrowhead,
