Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.04,0:37:56.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不对  是1349号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, 1349.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.61,0:37:58.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,女士  谁住这间房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ma'am, who lives in this apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.10,0:38:01.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,露丝  露丝·达文波特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That would be Ruth, Ruth Davenport.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.96,0:38:03.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我又想起一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.50,0:38:04.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么事  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's that, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.71,0:38:06.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,巴尼每次离开镇子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When Barney's out of town,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.21,0:38:08.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,都会把钥匙留给他兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he leaves the keys with his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.04,0:38:10.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,他兄弟是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And who would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.11,0:38:13.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.63,0:38:14.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've never met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.69,0:38:17.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,但汉克认识他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But Hank would know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.36,0:38:18.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,汉克是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.30,0:38:20.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,巴尼的朋友  汉克·菲尔莫尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Barney's friend, Hank Fillmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.63,0:38:22.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们去哪儿能找到汉克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where would we find Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.30,0:38:24.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.41,0:38:26.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,这会儿我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.08,0:38:29.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是我们这里的修理工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's our maintenance man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.74,0:38:31.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我刚才看到他回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I saw him out back a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.05,0:38:56.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Harvey?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.08,0:38:58.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈维  你个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Harvey, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.50,0:39:00.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是汉克吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.59,0:39:06.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们搞什么鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.39,0:39:09.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们是警察  菲尔莫尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Police, Mr. Fillmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.30,0:39:10.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你的协助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.74,0:39:11.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,是哈维叫你们来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did Harvey send you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.15,0:39:13.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔莫尔先生  我们急需\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Fillmore, we need a key
