Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.38,0:39:35.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道齐普的电话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, do you have a phone number for Chip?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.36,0:39:36.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no, no, no, no, no, no.
