Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.11,0:39:39.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,齐普不用电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chip ain't got no phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.54,0:39:43.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是等锁匠吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll wait for the locksmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.30,0:39:44.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.69,0:39:48.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许露丝出镇了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think that maybe Ruth's out of town?
