Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.95,0:39:50.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,实在是不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it would be a shame
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.91,0:39:52.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为她出远门的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'cause I'm supposed to water her plants
