Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.79,0:39:56.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有她房间钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.28,0:39:59.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.56,0:40:03.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我  我可以走了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Am I-- am I free to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.27,0:40:08.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  我可以走了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gentlemen, am--am I free to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.52,0:41:28.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈维  你这个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Harvey, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.87,0:41:31.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,是你把条子叫过来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you send the cops to my place of business?
