Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.47,0:41:34.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈维  是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Harvey-- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.85,0:41:36.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我拿到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I got it--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.47,0:41:37.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我全拿到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got all of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.71,0:41:39.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,就在手上  但这都是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}right here, but it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.33,0:41:40.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我和齐普的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mine and Chip's.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.04,0:41:43.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  你已经退出了  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. You opted out of this one, remember?
