Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.50,0:41:47.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,别恐吓我  哈维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}don't threaten me, Harvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.51,0:41:48.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Harvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.32,0:41:51.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Harvey?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.73,0:42:30.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,康斯坦丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Constance?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.92,0:42:34.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,为你高兴  戴夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good for you, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.88,0:42:37.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在改头换面了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're behaving yourself for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.25,0:42:39.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,过来帮下忙好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Want to help me with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.00,0:42:43.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very carefully.
