Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.58,0:44:06.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的木头要告诉你一条消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My log has a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.31,0:44:11.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我听着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.40,0:44:16.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我丢了点东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something is missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.19,0:44:19.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.80,0:44:22.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,线索就在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It has to do with
