Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.52,0:44:29.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.05,0:44:33.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The way you will find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.19,0:44:40.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,和你的遗产有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...has something to do with your heritage.
