Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.94,0:44:52.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  玛格丽特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.73,0:44:53.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
