Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.39,0:45:50.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dave?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.48,0:45:52.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dave!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.49,0:45:53.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,就来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.76,0:45:58.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你来看看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.99,0:46:01.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,头肯定是露丝·达文波特的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The head is definitely Ruth Davenport,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.19,0:46:02.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是住在公寓中的那个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the woman who lived in the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.17,0:46:05.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个无名男性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we've got a male John Doe.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.32,0:46:09.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知道这是谁的身体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't know whose body that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.73,0:46:11.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,查不出这些指纹是谁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing's come back on those prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.01,0:46:13.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是还有另一组指纹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there's another set of prints
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.00,0:46:14.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,遍布整间公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all over the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.57,0:46:15.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经查出来是谁的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we've got a hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.81,0:46:20.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,确定是属于本地人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a definite local hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.05,0:46:23.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尔·黑斯廷斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bill Hastings?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.78,0:46:26.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.58,0:46:27.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.65,0:46:29.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是我孩子的校长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's my kid's principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.08,0:47:14.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dave!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.11,0:47:16.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你来干什...  -菲莉斯  比尔在家吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What are you-- - Phyllis, is Bill home?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.86,0:47:18.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,-在  -谁来了  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - Who is it, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.60,0:47:20.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,是戴夫  戴夫·麦克利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's Dave, Dave Macklay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.99,0:47:26.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫  你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dave, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.55,0:47:27.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's going on, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.09,0:47:28.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bill, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.19,0:47:31.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我得逮捕你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna have to put you under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.32,0:47:35.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -请转过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What? - Please turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.14,0:47:37.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我得把你拷上  带你回局里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got to cuff you, and I've got to take you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.25,0:47:39.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, my God, Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.87,0:47:41.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不  这...  -天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No, it... - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.11,0:47:42.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,没事的  亲爱的  我什么坏事都没做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay, honey. I hav-- I haven't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.96,0:47:44.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我是因为什么事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could, uh--could you tell me what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.65,0:47:46.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在局里说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can talk about that at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.84,0:47:47.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟你一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.88,0:47:49.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,不不  待在家  他们肯定是搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, stay here. There's been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.02,0:47:51.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  我什么坏事都没干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right? I haven't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.92,0:47:53.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有权保持沉默\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.63,0:47:55.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,你所说的任何话都将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anything you say can and will be used
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.55,0:47:57.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,成为呈堂证供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}against you in a court of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.95,0:48:00.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,但摩根一家马上要来吃晚饭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But the Morgans are coming for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.11,0:48:01.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,你了解我刚说的权利吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you understand these rights I am--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.48,0:48:02.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我非常了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I understand perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.54,0:48:05.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,打给乔治说下我的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just call George and tell him where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.25,0:48:42.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说过有什么东西丢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She said something is missing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.08,0:48:45.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且和库柏探员有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it has to do with Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.07,0:48:52.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,但库柏探员失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But Agent Cooper is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.58,0:48:55.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,在沃利出世前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he hasn't been seen or heard from
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.74,0:48:57.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,都还没有他的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}since before Wally was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.35,0:48:59.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在沃利都24岁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Wally's 24 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.67,0:49:02.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,他和马龙·白兰度是一天生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was born on the same day as Marlon Brando.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.41,0:49:04.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,安迪想给他取名为马龙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andy wanted to name him Marlon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.40,0:49:07.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还没有收到过库柏探员的圣诞节贺卡呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we haven't even gotten a Christmas card from Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.21,0:49:08.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,他都没有见过沃利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He hasn't even seen Wally.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.83,0:49:11.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,安迪  露西  不早了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andy, Lucy, it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.16,0:49:15.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,去仓库把那些我刚才说的文件拿来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go down to storage and get those files that we talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.49,0:49:17.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,明早  把它们全都摆在桌面上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tomorrow morning, lay 'em all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.86,0:49:19.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会带咖啡和甜甜圈来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll bring the coffee and the doughnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.74,0:49:23.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  霍克副局长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, Deputy Chief Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.02,0:49:42.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dave?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.08,0:49:47.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,唐·哈里森   拉皮特城州警局的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don Harrison, State Police, Rapid City.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.54,0:49:49.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你来接手这个案子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hmm, are you taking this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.15,0:49:51.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是你的案子  戴夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's yours, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.31,0:49:52.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来帮忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.89,0:49:56.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,失踪的身体和头有消息了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any luck with the missing body and head?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.78,0:50:00.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.53,0:50:05.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,他关在这里多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How long's he been in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.03,0:50:08.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,差不多一个半小时了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.24,0:50:10.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,也差不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.83,0:50:13.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不想接这个案子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure you don't want to take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.40,0:50:18.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,迈克说你们两个是渔友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mike said you're fishing buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.01,0:50:20.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从高中起就认识他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've known him since high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.13,0:50:24.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,他对你估计会更坦诚一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He might tell you more than he'd tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.32,0:50:26.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,进去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.27,0:50:40.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉拖了这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I'm sorry about the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.18,0:50:41.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们有没有给你端杯咖啡什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, did they get you some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.37,0:50:43.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我喝水就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm good with the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.07,0:50:47.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you--can you, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.19,0:50:52.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,能不能告诉我出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can you please tell me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.24,0:50:56.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会说的  不过有几个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll get to that, but I have a few questions
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.05,0:50:58.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得先回答我一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I have to ask you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.93,0:51:05.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,你认不认识露丝·达文波特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know a Ruth Davenport?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.26,0:51:12.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,名字挺耳熟的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That name sounds familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.29,0:51:16.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,是那个图书管理员吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the librarian?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.01,0:51:18.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是的  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yes. - Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.13,0:51:18.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.11,0:51:21.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你认识她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.37,0:51:24.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,不大认识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.50,0:51:25.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,最多打个招呼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We say hello to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.24,0:51:29.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你最后一次见她是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When did you see her last?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.10,0:51:32.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.94,0:51:34.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我想想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.51,0:51:38.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,大概几个月前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe a couple months ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.32,0:51:47.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有去过露丝·达文波特的家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever been to Ruth Davenport's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.10,0:51:49.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  从没去过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. I've never been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.08,0:51:52.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我都...  我都不知道她家在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't--I don't--I don't even know where she lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.74,0:51:57.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有去过位于箭头路1349号的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever been to the apartment building
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.27,0:52:00.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,那栋公寓楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at 1349 Arrowhead Road?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.18,0:52:02.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.30,0:52:04.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,没去过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.86,0:52:09.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从来...  从来都没去过那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I--I've--I've never-- I've never been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.89,0:52:11.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,你...  你能不能告诉我这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could--could you please tell me what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.95,0:52:13.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,你拿到逮捕令了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you get the warrant?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.12,0:52:13.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,马上就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.48,0:52:15.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,法官在爬山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Judge was up the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.68,0:52:17.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.42,0:52:21.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能说说你在最近几天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can you account for your time
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.02,0:52:23.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,都干了些什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over the last three or four days?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.50,0:52:24.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  当然可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure, yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.33,0:52:26.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我工作日每天都在学校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, I've been at school every weekday.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.44,0:52:28.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,晚上呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And evenings?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.08,0:52:29.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的高中校长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our high-school principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.71,0:52:32.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,周三我放学之后直接回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, Wednesday, I went home right after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.59,0:52:35.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,周四的时候我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thursday, we had
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.12,0:52:38.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,在晚上开了个会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a-a meeting in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.01,0:52:39.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,之后...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.21,0:52:43.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...I went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.31,0:52:45.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.46,0:52:48.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,周五我去...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}uh, Friday, I went--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.66,0:52:50.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我出去吃了个晚饭  和菲莉斯一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I went out to dinner, Phyllis and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.39,0:52:52.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,吃完我们就直接回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we went home right after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.17,0:52:55.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我今天一整天都在家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And--and I was home all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.82,0:52:57.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What--what--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.65,0:53:00.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,周四的会是干什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what was this Thursday meeting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.54,0:53:02.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,关于授课的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Curriculum.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.66,0:53:04.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,教学评估\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}F-faculty evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.52,0:53:05.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,两个月开一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a bimonthly meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.40,0:53:07.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候结束的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when did it end?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.80,0:53:11.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,大概是九点半吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Around 9:30, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.29,0:53:13.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也记不清了  我们还点了披萨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know. We ordered pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.56,0:53:16.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,那...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.90,0:53:20.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你之后就直接回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you went home directly after?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.26,0:53:21.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.48,0:53:24.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你几点到的家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what time did you get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.09,0:53:27.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,十点十五  二十左右吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At 10:15, 10:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.46,0:53:33.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,你一般回家要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, how long does it take you to drive home usually?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.15,0:53:46.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}周四会议\N9点30结束  10点15到10点20到家
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.61,0:53:47.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yeah--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.47,0:53:50.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,对了  我想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}oh, yeah, now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.70,0:53:53.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我把...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I gave...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.84,0:53:57.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的秘书  贝蒂  送回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...my assistant, Betty, a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.19,0:54:01.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,她当时有点...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something wrong with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.23,0:54:05.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,她的车出了点毛病...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}car, something wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.94,0:54:16.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想和乔治说句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think I'd like to speak to George.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.94,0:54:19.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.02,0:54:22.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,他...  他来了没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is--is--is--is he--is he-- is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.47,0:54:25.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can check.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.74,0:54:33.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过比尔  在把律师叫来之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But, Bill, is there anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.13,0:54:35.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还有没有别的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that you would like to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.05,0:54:37.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,想要跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before we get the lawyer involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.78,0:54:49.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,请你告诉我到底出了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.61,0:54:58.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,露丝·达文波特被谋杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ruth Davenport was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.01,0:55:01.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,她的公寓里到处都是你的指纹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And your prints are all over her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.82,0:55:13.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.46,0:55:16.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.85,0:55:24.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,带黑斯廷斯先生去他的新房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Show Mr. Hastings to his new room.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.92,0:55:26.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,他可以在那见他的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He can meet with his lawyer there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.47,0:55:31.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  你现在得跟我走了  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, you're gonna have to come with me now, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.62,0:55:34.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.60,0:55:58.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,左边  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To the left here, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.52,0:56:06.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right--right here, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.59,0:56:18.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dave,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.52,0:56:20.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能联系一下菲莉斯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}could I speak to Phyllis?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.13,0:56:22.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能让我  让我和她谈谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could you let me-- could you let me do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.96,0:56:26.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看看能做些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.65,0:57:05.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,黑斯廷斯夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mrs. Hastings,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.80,0:57:07.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有你房子的搜查令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we have a warrant to search your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.91,0:57:11.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.10,0:57:13.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们今晚还要招待客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have guests for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.88,0:57:15.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,车道上的是比尔的车吗  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that Bill's car in the driveway, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.59,0:57:17.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,是沃尔沃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the Volvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.13,0:57:19.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要用一下钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll need the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.44,0:57:21.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dave?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.64,0:57:23.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,必须这么做  菲莉斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It has to be done, Phyllis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.48,0:57:34.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.36,0:57:41.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.37,0:58:18.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的手电筒坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My flashlight's broke.
